FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Got questions? We've got answers. Check out our FAQs below.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How does the food ordering process work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Simply browse our menu, select your desired items, add them to your cart, and proceed to checkout. You can choose delivery or pickup options before completing your order.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: What payment methods do you accept?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: We accept major credit cards, debit cards, and popular mobile payment methods like Apple Pay and Google Pay for your convenience.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: How long does delivery usually take?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Delivery times vary depending on your location and the restaurant's preparation time. On average, you can expect your order within 30-45 minutes.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Absolutely! Many of our menu items offer customization options. Look for the 'Customize' button when selecting your food to make changes or add special instructions.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Do you cater to dietary restrictions?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Yes, we offer a variety of options for different dietary needs. You can filter menu items by categories such as vegetarian, vegan, gluten-free, and more to find suitable choices.
PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Tasty Questions? We've Got Delicious Answers!
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does our food app work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app connects you with local restaurants, showcases their menus, and allows you to order food for delivery or pickup with just a few taps. It's like having a whole city's worth of cuisine right at your fingertips!
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Is there a minimum order amount?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Minimum order amounts vary by restaurant. You can easily see any minimum requirements on each restaurant's page before placing your order. We strive to offer options for every budget and appetite!
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: How long does delivery usually take?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Delivery times depend on factors like distance, traffic, and restaurant preparation time. On average, most orders arrive within 30-45 minutes. You'll see an estimated delivery time when you place your order, and you can track its progress in real-time!
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Can I customize my meal or make special requests?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Absolutely! Many restaurants offer customization options right in the app. You can also add special instructions for your order. Whether you're dealing with allergies, preferences, or just feeling creative, we'll do our best to accommodate your culinary wishes!
